<Algorithm code="                 1. For each Cyclic Module Record _m_ of _module_.[[AsyncParentModules]], do                   1. If _execList_ does not contain _m_ and _m_.[[CycleRoot]].[[EvaluationError]] is ~empty~, then                     1. Assert: _m_.[[Status]] is ~evaluating-async~.                     1. Assert: _m_.[[EvaluationError]] is ~empty~.                     1. Assert: _m_.[[AsyncEvaluationOrder]] is an integer.                     1. Assert: _m_.[[PendingAsyncDependencies]] &gt; 0.                     1. Set _m_.[[PendingAsyncDependencies]] to _m_.[[PendingAsyncDependencies]] - 1.                     1. If _m_.[[PendingAsyncDependencies]] = 0, then                       1. Append _m_ to _execList_.                       1. If _m_.[[HasTLA]] is *false*, perform GatherAvailableAncestors(_m_, _execList_).                 1. Return ~unused~.               ">
